<p>The wholesale prices of medicines for chronic hepatitis C are listed below. Wholesale prices are the prices paid by pharmacies.</p>
<p>The cost to you for each medicine depends on your health insurance, the dose (amount) you need to take, and whether the medicine comes in a generic form.</p>
